summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of seventy-four and 52/100 dollars ($74.52) or so much thereof as may be necessary from the Cedar River Watershed Condemnation Fund of The City of Seattle, for the purpose of paying the City's portion of the 1911 general taxes on certain property, towit: Sections 1, 3, 4, 10, T 21, R 8; 3, 4, 5, 9, 10, 11, 15, 17, 23, 25 T 22, R 8; 31, T 23, R 8.
